@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录获取令牌
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询 AppHost 资源库（全部，不含 agent/app）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 资源库 9 类 + 来源（知识库-官方，应对齐种子 4 条）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&resourceType=knowledge-base&source=official
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 知识库-自定义（无官方数据时期望为空或仅用户数据）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&resourceType=knowledge-base&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 子类型：知识库-文本
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&resourceType=knowledge-base&subType=text&source=official
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 各类一行（resourceType slug）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=plugin&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=workflow&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=database&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=prompt&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=card&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=memory&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library?pageIndex=1&pageSize=2&resourceType=voice&source=custom
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建音色（自定义来源）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/voice-assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试音色",
  "description": "dev",
  "language": "zh-CN",
  "gender": "female",
  "previewUrl": null
}

### 导入 AppHost 资源库文件
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library/imports
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "workflow",
  "libraryItemId": 1,
  "targetAppId": 1
}

### 复制 AppHost 资源到资源库
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library/exports
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "plugin",
  "resourceId": 1
}

### 移动 AppHost 资源到资源库
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workspaces/library/moves
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "knowledge-base",
  "resourceId": 1
}
